OL,3,CStormont and government urged to end
OL,4,C'penny-pinching betrayal of policing'
OL,6,FThe chairman of the Police Federation
OL,7,Ffor Northern Ireland has called on the
OL,8,FUK Government and the Stormont
OL,9,FExecutive to end their "shameful,
OL,10,Fpenny-pinching betrayal of policing".
OL,12,FLiam Kelly, in his address to the
OL,13,Ffederation's annual conference in Co
OL,14,FAntrim, said the PSNI is in the
OL,15,Fdeepest resourcing crisis since its
OL,16,Finception and warned that officer
OL,17,Fnumbers will slide towards 6,000
OL,18,Funless there is urgent intervention.
OL,26,@qD@XOUrD@dO]
