OL,3,CStormont and government urged to end
OL,4,C'penny-pinching betrayal of policing'
OL,6,FMr Kelly said there is an #80million
OL,7,Fdeficit in the PSNI budget, which
OL,8,Fmeans the organisation will have to
OL,9,F"drastically pare back services".
OL,11,FThe Stormont Assembly voted this week
OL,12,Fto back this year's budget, although
OL,13,FJustice Minister Naomi Long has
OL,14,Fpreviously warned that the allocation
OL,15,Fgiven to her department will have a
OL,16,Fdetrimental impact on services.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@`O]
