OL,3,CStormont and government urged to end
OL,4,C'penny-pinching betrayal of policing'
OL,6,FMr Kelly said: "We will not stop until
OL,7,Fwe convince the government and the
OL,8,FExecutive to end their shameful, penny-
OL,9,Fpinching betrayal of policing in
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland and, more
OL,11,Fspecifically, the men and women of the
OL,12,FPSNI who put themselves in harm's way
OL,13,Fevery day for the benefit of our
OL,14,Fsociety."
OL,16,FHe added: "There is an abject failure
OL,17,Fto properly fund and resource policing.
OL,26,@nD@POUvD@IO]xD@KOU
