OL,3,CStormont and government urged to end
OL,4,C'penny-pinching betrayal of policing'
OL,6,FHe said: "The drip-drip erosion has to
OL,7,Fend.
OL,9,F"Too few 'folks on the hill' have our
OL,10,Fback the way they really should.
OL,12,F"We want them to go to the next
OL,13,Flevel... to say that we are being
OL,14,Fdecimated numerically and that the
OL,15,Fmoney that's allocated is insufficient.
OL,17,F"This is a battle that must be waged
OL,18,Fin Whitehall and Westminster.
