OL,3,CStormont and government urged to end
OL,4,C'penny-pinching betrayal of policing'
OL,6,F"Collectively, the Government's more
OL,7,Finclined to listen to ministers from
OL,8,Fhere ` although there's no guarantee
OL,9,Fthey will ` than they appear willing
OL,10,Fto listen to the Chief Constable or
OL,11,Fthis federation."
OL,13,FMr Kelly told the conference in
OL,14,FTemplepatrick that departures from the
OL,15,FPSNI mean the force will slide towards
OL,16,F6,000 officers by either the end of
OL,17,Fthis year or the end of the current
OL,18,Ffinancial year.
