OL,3,CStormont and government urged to end
OL,4,C'penny-pinching betrayal of policing'
OL,6,FHe said: "This will make our ability
OL,7,Fto respond effectively nigh on
OL,8,Fimpossible, and without positive
OL,9,Fintervention the crisis in policing
OL,10,Fwill continue to get worse.
OL,12,F"One officer per 320 of the population
OL,13,Fis wholly inadequate to meet the
OL,14,Fmultiplicity of challenges that are
OL,15,Fout there. Great damage is being done
OL,16,Fand it is dangerous and irresponsible.
OL,26,@nD@JOUtD@AOU
