OL,3,CStormont and government urged to end
OL,4,C'penny-pinching betrayal of policing'
OL,6,FHe added: "We must have stronger
OL,7,Fpenalties and meaningful custodial
OL,8,Fsentences to deter would-be attackers.
OL,10,F"They must be left in no doubt and
OL,11,Fmade to think twice before carrying
OL,12,Fout assaults.
OL,14,F"We have to drive down these
OL,15,Funacceptable assault figures."
OL,17,FTurning to the issue of police pay, Mr
OL,18,FKelly said: "Let me be clear: any
OL,19,Fattempt to break with core pay spine
OL,20,Fparity with our England and Wales
OL,21,Fcolleagues would be a retrograde step.
